#. SetStartDupes.STRINGS.UI.DUPEEDITING.DETAILS.CONTENT.SCROLLRECTCONTAINER.TRAITINTERESTCONTAINER.CONTENT.GRP2.ADDTRAITBUTTON.TOOLTIP
msgctxt "SetStartDupes.STRINGS.UI.DUPEEDITING.DETAILS.CONTENT.SCROLLRECTCONTAINER.TRAITINTERESTCONTAINER.CONTENT.GRP2.ADDTRAITBUTTON.TOOLTIP"
msgid "Choose another trait to add to the duplicant"
msgstr "복제체에게 추가할 특성을 선택하십시오."

#. SetStartDupes.STRINGS.UI.DUPEEDITING.DETAILS.CONTENT.SCROLLRECTCONTAINER.TRAITINTERESTCONTAINER.DESCRIPTOR.INTERESTLABEL
msgctxt "SetStartDupes.STRINGS.UI.DUPEEDITING.DETAILS.CONTENT.SCROLLRECTCONTAINER.TRAITINTERESTCONTAINER.DESCRIPTOR.INTERESTLABEL"
